      <title>白宫称周六将对中国、墨西哥、加拿大征收关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/white-house-says-china-mexico-canada-tariffs-to-hit-saturday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫表示，总统唐纳德·特朗普打算于周六推进对墨西哥和加拿大征收 25% 关税、对中国征收 10% 关税的计划，并否认了有关他计划将实施时间推迟一个月的报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/white-house-says-china-mexico-canada-tariffs-to-hit-saturday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 18:25:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车石墨关税之争将考验马斯克对特朗普的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/tesla-fights-tariffs-on-ev-graphite-putting-musk-at-odds-with-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃隆·马斯克的特斯拉公司正在带头阻止对中国进口石墨征收新关税，这使得唐纳德·特朗普最富有的支持者与总统最喜欢的经济工具发生冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/tesla-fights-tariffs-on-ev-graphite-putting-musk-at-odds-with-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 16:51:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国领跑者遭遇移民大失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-front-runner-merz-suffers-blow-with-migration-bill-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国保守党领袖弗里德里希·梅尔茨在极右翼的支持下推动严格的移民法案，但在紧张的议会投票中失败，导致其竞选总理的进程遭遇重大挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/german-front-runner-merz-suffers-blow-with-migration-bill-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 16:17:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普特使格雷内尔访问委内瑞拉讨论美国囚犯和帮派成员问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-envoy-grenell-set-to-meet-venezuela-s-maduro-on-prisoners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼古拉斯·马杜罗寻求重启与美国的谈判，唐纳德·特朗普总统的一名顾问将会见委内瑞拉政府官员，这是两个意识形态对手多年来最高级别的会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-envoy-grenell-set-to-meet-venezuela-s-maduro-on-prisoners</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 16:06:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大因诉讼和政治不确定性推迟资本利得税改革至 2026 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-delays-capital-gains-tax-change-to-2026-amid-lawsuits-politics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于该措施面临法律挑战且遭到主要政界人士的否认，加拿大将把资本利得纳入税率的提高推迟到2026年1月。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/canada-delays-capital-gains-tax-change-to-2026-amid-lawsuits-politics</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 15:58:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿斯利康因英国资金问题取消疫苗中心投资</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/astrazeneca-calls-off-vaccine-hub-investment-over-uk-funding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在与英国新工党政府就该疫苗生产厂的政府资助金额问题发生长期争论后，阿斯利康公司放弃了向英国一家疫苗生产厂投资 4.5 亿英镑（5.58 亿美元）的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/astrazeneca-calls-off-vaccine-hub-investment-over-uk-funding</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:47:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达首席执行官黄仁勋将于周五在白宫会见特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-ceo-huang-to-meet-trump-at-white-house-on-friday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国准备对半导体征收关税、权衡补贴计划的命运并调查中国人工智能初创公司 DeepSeek 是否绕过出口管制获取该芯片制造商的产品之际，唐纳德·特朗普总统将于周五在白宫会见英伟达公司首席执行官黄仁勋。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/nvidia-ceo-huang-to-meet-trump-at-white-house-on-friday</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 14:28:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的资助禁令两天内结束，引发持续恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-s-federal-funding-freeze-sparks-lasting-panic-despite-omb-reversal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统连续一周发布行政命令后，这份备忘录于周一晚间发布，不到 48 小时后被撤销。但暂停所有联邦贷款和补助的命令在全国范围内引起了反响，从小型非营利组织到庞大的卫生机构。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-s-federal-funding-freeze-sparks-lasting-panic-despite-omb-reversal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雪佛龙开始使用“美国湾”来向特朗普致敬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chevron-starts-using-gulf-of-america-in-nod-to-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令美国重新命名该水域后，雪佛龙公司开始使用“美国湾”而不是“墨西哥湾”来描述其部分最大石油业务所在地。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/chevron-starts-using-gulf-of-america-in-nod-to-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 12:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普为就职典礼从加密货币公司筹集了数百万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-raised-millions-from-crypto-firms-for-his-inauguration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[最新披露的信息显示，唐纳德·特朗普总统的就职委员会从加密货币行业的公司那里获得了数百万美元的捐款，而加密货币行业已经受到了特朗普政府的特别关注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-31/trump-raised-millions-from-crypto-firms-for-his-inauguration</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 31 Jan 2025 01:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
